events.title: Outlander
events.description: The War Within is World of Warcraft's latest expansion, revealed on November 3, 2023 and launching on August 26, 2024. This is WoW's tenth expansion, and introduces new features including Delves, Warbands, class-specific Hero Talent trees, the new Earthen allied race, Skyriding, and 4 new zones. Here is a compilation of everything new to The War Within expansion.
